## MCP servers in this workspace (prefer tools over guessing)

Before any MCP call, read that tool’s schema from Cursor’s MCP tool list or the local MCP descriptor files for the enabled server (do not guess parameters).

### `plugin-firebase-firebase` (Firebase)

- Not used by Tabocalypse core; if you add Firebase, call **`firebase_get_environment`** first, follow **firebase-basics**, and read tool schemas before calls.

### `user-eamodio.gitlens-extension-GitKraken` (GitLens / GitKraken)

- Use for **git status/log/diff**, branches, PRs when connected; pass the repo **`directory`** argument tools require.

